<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="iddc5b080f-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06" identifier="/us/usc/t12/s1795i"><num value="1795i">§ 1795i.</num><heading> Annual report</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The annual report required by <ref href="/us/usc/t12/s1752a/d">section 1752a(d) of this title</ref> shall include a full report of the activities of the Facility.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="iddc5b0810-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06">(<ref href="/us/act/1934-06-26/ch750">June 26, 1934, ch. 750</ref>, title III, formerly subch. III, § 310, as added <ref href="/us/pl/95/630/tXVIII/s1802">Pub. L. 95–630, title XVIII, § 1802</ref>, <date date="1978-11-10">Nov. 10, 1978</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/92/3723">92 Stat. 3723</ref>; amended <ref href="/us/pl/96/221/tIII/s309/b/1">Pub. L. 96–221, title III, § 309(b)(1)</ref>, <date date="1980-03-31">Mar. 31, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/149">94 Stat. 149</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/109/351/tVII/s726/27">Pub. L. 109–351, title VII, § 726(27)</ref>, <date date="2006-10-13">Oct. 13, 2006</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/120/2003">120 Stat. 2003</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="iddc5b0811-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06">
